==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wrongness
<hw>Wrong"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state of being
wrong; wrongfulness; error; fault.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The best great <qex>wrongnesses</qex> within themselves.</q>
<rj><qau>Bp. Butler.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The rightness or <qex>wrongness</qex> of this view.</q>
<rj><qau>Latham.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wrongous</ent>⟦br⟧
